      • isCorrectlyLoggedIn

        public static boolean isCorrectlyLoggedIn(java.lang.String sessionID,
                          java.lang.String email)
        Returns true if the user (email) is correctly logged in (the sessionIDs are identically)
        Parameters:
        sessionID - should be the actual sessionID of the Browser-Session. Can be get through session("uuid") by a class extended with play.mavc.Contoller
        email - identifier of the user. Is stored in cookies (session("email")) too.
        Returns:
        answer
